  "<h3>War Thunder Dashboard  v{version}</h3><p>基于 PyQt6 的战争雷霆实时战术看板。通过游戏内置 8111 端口 API 读取战场数据，在副屏或局域网其他设备上显示实时地图、单位追踪、态势感知与 HUD 消息。</p><p><a href='https://github.com/HYLiangSheng/WTDashboard' style='color:#7ec8e3;'>github.com/HYLiangSheng/WTDashboard</a></p><hr style='border-color:#3a3a5c;'><p style='color:#aaaacc; font-size:10px;'>欢迎提交 Issue、功能建议或参与贡献。许可证：MIT</p>": "<h3>War Thunder Dashboard  v{version}</h3><p>A real-time War Thunder tactical display built with PyQt6. Reads battlefield data via the in-game 8111 port API, showing a live map, unit tracking, situation report, and HUD messages on a secondary monitor or LAN device.</p><p><a href='https://github.com/HYLiangSheng/WTDashboard' style='color:#7ec8e3;'>github.com/HYLiangSheng/WTDashboard</a></p><hr style='border-color:#3a3a5c;'><p style='color:#aaaacc; font-size:10px;'>Issues, feature requests, and contributions are welcome. License: MIT</p>"
